localedata.title: TRAVERSE
localedata.description: The Traverse action represents the presentation of the navigation element without content.

localedata.title: VIEW
localedata.description: The View action represents the presentation of the content or meta-information of a resource.

localedata.title: PERSONALIZE
localedata.description: The Personalize action represents all modifications to a resource that are only visible to the owner of a resource.

localedata.title: EDIT
localedata.description: The Edit action represents all modifications to a resource (e.g. changing the meta-information of a resource) that are visible not only to the owner of a resource.

localedata.title: ADD_PRIVATE_CHILD
localedata.description: The Add Private Child action represents the creation of a new private resource underneath an existing resource that can be accessed by a single user only.

localedata.title: ADD_CHILD
localedata.description: The Add Child action represents the creation of a new shared resource underneath an existing resource.

localedata.title: DELETE
localedata.description: The Delete action represents the deletion of a resource or the removal of a resource from its parent resource (e.g. when a resource is moved from one place in the topology to an other).

localedata.title: GRANT_ACCESS
localedata.description: The Grant Access On action represents the activity of granting other principals access on a specific resource.

localedata.title: DELEGATE
localedata.description: The Delegate To action represents the activity of delegating access on resources to a specific principal.

localedata.title: DISCONNECT
localedata.description: This Action represents the disconnection of specific resources from the portal.

localedata.title: RUN_AS_USER
localedata.description: This Action represents impersonating a user.

localedata.title: EDIT_MARKUP
localedata.description: The Edit Markup action represents all modifications to static pages and mashups.
